snippet.title: Inseparable
snippet.description:
Hello Guys !
Kindly welcome all. Finally I am sharing my game project! 🎉The game called Inseparable. This is my first big project like this and I am very proud of what I already done. Still there is some things to do but I hope we will go through them together💪
Sit, relax and enjoy the video🍿✌️
More info on the Website - https://inseparablethegame.wixsite.com/inseparable
If you like this project, I will be very grateful for follow my IG account - this is my main place of posting all info and materials. https://www.instagram.com/inseparablethegame/
Also let me know what you think about this. It will be nice to know your opinions.
If You like and wanna help me a bit pls share the video, not much work for you, much help for me :)
